🧭 Navigation Flow
Automated Employee Onboarding & Offboarding System

This defines how users (HR, IT, Managers, Employees, Admins) move through the system UI and backend workflows during the employee lifecycle.

1. Core Navigation Structure

The system is typically organized into these main modules:

Dashboard
Employees
Onboarding
Offboarding
Access Control
Documents
Workflows
Audit Logs
Settings
