3. Onboarding Navigation Flow (End-to-End)
HR Adds Employee
  ↓
System Validates Data
  ↓
Workflow Triggered (NEW_HIRE event)
  ↓
IT Provisioning Queue
  ↓
Access Granted (Email, Tools)
  ↓
Manager Assignment
  ↓
Employee Checklist Activated
  ↓
Training + Documentation
  ↓
Onboarding Completed
4. Offboarding Navigation Flow
Exit Request Created
  ↓
Manager Approval
  ↓
HR Confirmation
  ↓
Workflow Triggered (EXIT_APPROVED)
  ↓
IT Revokes Access
  ↓
Asset Return Tracking
  ↓
Payroll Finalization
  ↓
Data Archival
  ↓
Employee Status = EXITED
